  3. Grimme, S.; Antony, J.; Ehrlich, S.; Krieg, H.
     A consistent and accurate ab initio parametrization of density functional dispersion correction (DFT-D) for the 94 elements H-Pu
     J. Chem. Phys. 2010 132 , 154104
